1. Take an ans variable to store result.
2. We can buy pen/ pencil in various number of ways from (0 to total//cost), So we need to calculate all the combination of one article with other. For this we will get a for loop from 0 to total/cost.
3. Then for each value we ca calculate the number of ways to buy other item, i.e also from 0 to remaining_amount/cost.
4. To calculate that we can just calculate the sum of n natural numbers +1 for 0.

